host_templates._comment:
{FR: Modèle pour superviser les équipements Stormshield en SNMP}
{EN: Template to check Stormshield devices using SNMP protocol}
host_templates.alias: Template to check Stormshield devices using SNMP protocol
host_templates.name: Net-Stormshield-SNMP

information.author: Centreon

description.value:
Plugin pack to monitor Stormshield network equipment via SNMP:
* Connections
* Cpu
* Cpu-Detailed
* Disk
* Ha-status
* Hardware
* Health
* Load
* Memory
* QoS
* Swap
* Traffic (by interface name, ID or all interfaces)
* Vpn-Status

Plugin pack pour surveiller les équipements réseau Stormshield via SNMP :
* Connections
* Cpu
* Cpu-Detailed
* Disk
* Ha-status
* Hardware
* Health
* Load
* Memory
* QoS
* Swap
* Traffic (by interface name, ID or all interfaces)
* Vpn-Status

information.monitoring_procedure:
# The documentation page of this Plugin-Pack requires a newer version of the Plugin Pack Manager module:

* 20.04.0 or later

information.name: Stormshield SNMP
